---
const siteTitle = "Amorphing · Responsive Brand Design";
const siteDescription = "AI-native brand systems that morph across ventures, languages, and contexts. Built with parametric design, SSOT principles, and radical transparency.";
const baseUrl = "https://amorphing.com";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />

	<!-- Primary Meta Tags -->
	<title>{siteTitle}</title>
	<meta name="title" content={siteTitle} />
	<meta name="description" content={siteDescription} />

	<!-- Open Graph / Facebook -->
	<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
	<meta property="og:url" content={baseUrl} />
	<meta property="og:title" content={siteTitle} />
	<meta property="og:description" content={siteDescription} />

	<!-- Twitter -->
	<meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
	<meta property="twitter:url" content={baseUrl} />
	<meta property="twitter:title" content={siteTitle} />
	<meta property="twitter:description" content={siteDescription} />

	<!-- Fonts -->
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Slab:wght@300;400;600;700&family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

	<!-- Favicon -->
	<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />

	<!-- JSON-LD Structured Data -->
	<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
		"@context": "https://schema.org",
		"@type": "Organization",
		"name": "Amorphing",
		"description": "AI-native brand systems that morph across contexts",
		"url": baseUrl,
		"logo": `${baseUrl}/logo.svg`,
		"sameAs": []
	})} />
</head>
<body>
	<main>
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="hero">
			<div class="logo-container">
				<svg class="logo" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
					<!-- Circle -->
					<circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" fill="#8b5cf6" />
					<!-- Letter A (centered) -->
					<text x="100" y="100"
					      font-family="Roboto Slab, serif"
					      font-size="120"
					      font-weight="600"
					      fill="white"
					      text-anchor="middle"
					      dominant-baseline="central">A</text>
				</svg>
				<h1 class="venture-name">Amorphing</h1>
			</div>

			<p class="tagline">Responsive Brand Design</p>
			<p class="description">{siteDescription}</p>
		</section>

		<!-- The 5 Pillars -->
		<section class="pillars">
			<h2>The 5 Pillars of Amorphic Design</h2>

			<div class="pillar-grid">
				<article class="pillar">
					<h3>1. Data Transparency</h3>
					<p>Every design decision is traceable to source data (LAB, RAL, WCAG). No magic, no guessing.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="pillar">
					<h3>2. Parametric Everything</h3>
					<p>One input generates infinite variants. Colors, logos, layouts morph from shared DNA.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="pillar">
					<h3>3. No Decoration</h3>
					<p>Form follows function. Geometric primitives (circles, lines, grids). Beauty emerges from constraints.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="pillar">
					<h3>4. Accessibility First</h3>
					<p>WCAG AAA by default. Design systems that work for everyone, everywhere.</p>
				</article>

				<article class="pillar">
					<h3>5. Modular DNA</h3>
					<p>Ventures inherit core traits, express unique phenotypes. One OS, infinite organisms.</p>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Showcase: 4 Ventures -->
		<section class="ventures">
			<h2>Built with Amorphing</h2>
			<p class="ventures-desc">Four ventures, one design DNA. Watch as brand identity morphs across contexts:</p>

			<div class="venture-grid">
				<div class="venture-card" style="--venture-color: #ff6b35;">
					<svg class="venture-logo" viewBox="0 0 120 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<circle cx="60" cy="60" r="54" fill="#ff6b35" />
						<text x="60" y="60"
						      font-family="Roboto Slab, serif"
						      font-size="72"
						      font-weight="600"
						      fill="white"
						      text-anchor="middle"
						      dominant-baseline="central">b</text>
					</svg>
					<h3>brainfruit</h3>
					<p>Venture Builder · Orange</p>
				</div>

				<div class="venture-card" style="--venture-color: #3399ff;">
					<svg class="venture-logo" viewBox="0 0 120 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<circle cx="60" cy="60" r="54" fill="#3399ff" />
						<text x="60" y="60"
						      font-family="Roboto Slab, serif"
						      font-size="72"
						      font-weight="600"
						      fill="white"
						      text-anchor="middle"
						      dominant-baseline="central">P</text>
					</svg>
					<h3>PRIMOVIVO</h3>
					<p>Interior Design · Blue</p>
				</div>

				<div class="venture-card" style="--venture-color: #8b5cf6;">
					<svg class="venture-logo" viewBox="0 0 120 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<circle cx="60" cy="60" r="54" fill="#8b5cf6" />
						<text x="60" y="60"
						      font-family="Roboto Slab, serif"
						      font-size="72"
						      font-weight="600"
						      fill="white"
						      text-anchor="middle"
						      dominant-baseline="central">A</text>
					</svg>
					<h3>Amorphing</h3>
					<p>Brand Design · Purple</p>
				</div>

				<div class="venture-card" style="--venture-color: #10b981;">
					<svg class="venture-logo" viewBox="0 0 120 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<circle cx="60" cy="60" r="54" fill="#10b981" />
						<text x="60" y="60"
						      font-family="Roboto Slab, serif"
						      font-size="72"
						      font-weight="600"
						      fill="white"
						      text-anchor="middle"
						      dominant-baseline="central">V</text>
					</svg>
					<h3>Venture 04</h3>
					<p>Coming Soon · Emerald</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="cta">
			<h2>Ready to morph your brand?</h2>
			<p>Amorphing is in private beta. Request early access:</p>
			<a href="mailto:hello@amorphing.com" class="cta-button">hello@amorphing.com</a>
		</section>

		<!-- Footer -->
		<footer>
			<p>© 2026 Amorphing · Part of <a href="https://brainfruit.de">brainfruit</a> · Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a></p>
			<p class="footer-meta">Open Source · AI-Native · WCAG AAA</p>
		</footer>
	</main>

	<style>
		:root {
			--purple: #8b5cf6;
			--purple-dark: #7c3aed;
			--gray-50: #f9fafb;
			--gray-100: #f3f4f6;
			--gray-200: #e5e7eb;
			--gray-700: #374151;
			--gray-800: #1f2937;
			--gray-900: #111827;
			--spacing: 8px;
		}

		* {
			margin: 0;
			padding: 0;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}

		body {
			font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
			line-height: 1.6;
			color: var(--gray-800);
			background: var(--gray-50);
		}

		main {
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
		}

		/* Hero Section */
		.hero {
			text-align: center;
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 12) 0 calc(var(--spacing) * 8);
		}

		.logo-container {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			gap: calc(var(--spacing) * 3);
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
		}

		.logo {
			width: 120px;
			height: 120px;
			filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 16px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3));
		}

		.venture-name {
			font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;
			font-size: 4rem;
			font-weight: 600;
			color: var(--purple);
			margin: 0;
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			font-weight: 500;
			color: var(--gray-700);
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
		}

		.description {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
			color: var(--gray-700);
			max-width: 700px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}

		/* Pillars Section */
		.pillars {
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 8) 0;
			background: white;
			border-radius: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 6);
		}

		.pillars h2 {
			font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 6);
			color: var(--gray-900);
		}

		.pillar-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
			gap: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
			padding: 0 calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
		}

		.pillar {
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 3);
			border-left: 4px solid var(--purple);
		}

		.pillar h3 {
			font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
			color: var(--purple);
		}

		.pillar p {
			color: var(--gray-700);
			line-height: 1.7;
		}

		/* Ventures Section */
		.ventures {
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 8) 0;
		}

		.ventures h2 {
			font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			text-align: center;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
			color: var(--gray-900);
		}

		.ventures-desc {
			text-align: center;
			font-size: 1.125rem;
			color: var(--gray-700);
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 6);
		}

		.venture-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
			gap: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
		}

		.venture-card {
			background: white;
			border-radius: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
			text-align: center;
			border: 2px solid var(--gray-200);
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.venture-card:hover {
			border-color: var(--venture-color);
			box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
			transform: translateY(-4px);
		}

		.venture-logo {
			width: 80px;
			height: 80px;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
		}

		.venture-card h3 {
			font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;
			font-size: 1.5rem;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing));
			color: var(--gray-900);
		}

		.venture-card p {
			color: var(--gray-700);
			font-size: 0.875rem;
		}

		/* CTA Section */
		.cta {
			text-align: center;
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 10) calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple) 0%, var(--purple-dark) 100%);
			border-radius: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
			color: white;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 6);
		}

		.cta h2 {
			font-family: 'Roboto Slab', serif;
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 2);
		}

		.cta p {
			font-size: 1.25rem;
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
			opacity: 0.95;
		}

		.cta-button {
			display: inline-block;
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 2) calc(var(--spacing) * 4);
			background: white;
			color: var(--purple);
			text-decoration: none;
			border-radius: calc(var(--spacing));
			font-weight: 600;
			font-size: 1.125rem;
			transition: all 0.3s ease;
		}

		.cta-button:hover {
			background: var(--gray-100);
			transform: scale(1.05);
		}

		/* Footer */
		footer {
			text-align: center;
			padding: calc(var(--spacing) * 4) 0;
			color: var(--gray-700);
			border-top: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
		}

		footer p {
			margin-bottom: calc(var(--spacing));
		}

		footer a {
			color: var(--purple);
			text-decoration: none;
		}

		footer a:hover {
			text-decoration: underline;
		}

		.footer-meta {
			font-size: 0.875rem;
			color: var(--gray-700);
		}

		/* Responsive */
		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.venture-name {
				font-size: 2.5rem;
			}

			.logo {
				width: 80px;
				height: 80px;
			}

			.pillars h2,
			.ventures h2,
			.cta h2 {
				font-size: 2rem;
			}

			.pillar-grid,
			.venture-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
		}
	</style>
</body>
</html>
